01:01:17.040 --> 01:01:24.011
Look, Cousin Joe is back. My goodness, look at him. He has been gone for how many years?

01:01:24.012 --> 01:01:30.173
I want to tell you there is a heaven to gain and a hell to shun. Do you understand?

01:01:30.174 --> 01:01:47.838
How many unbelievers are going to become believers immediately because they see Uncle Joe, who died a couple years ago, come back and tell them that Jesus Christ is real as a witness?

01:01:47.839 --> 01:01:58.730
You said, Brandon, you are way out there. Yeah, I am. I believe for big because I know I have a big God.

01:01:58.731 --> 01:02:04.875
Too many people have labored to put Him in a box. They put Him in a little box. They say, This is where you are, Lord.

01:02:04.876 --> 01:02:09.729
You have to do it because this is what my religious theology degree told me you can do.

01:02:09.730 --> 01:02:15.706
I do not have a degree. All I have is Jesus, and He comes and visits me. I tell you, it is the truth.

01:02:15.707 --> 01:02:28.558
Jesus Christ is coming, ladies and gentlemen, and you better get your heart right before Him or you are going to get left. I yell because I am passionate about it.

01:02:28.559 --> 01:02:34.897
Most people are asleep and they do not realize the signs of the times of the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ are all around us.

01:02:34.898 --> 01:02:47.519
He just wants people to rise up and say, Who will go? Who can I send into the nations to tell them about My coming?

01:02:47.520 --> 01:02:55.884
Signs and wonders will follow them that believe. Will you believe? I choose to believe.

01:02:55.885 --> 01:03:06.479
That is why I said even when I saw the dead being raised and saw those bones coming back to life, I said, Lord, I believe, help my unbelief.

01:03:06.480 --> 01:03:11.406
In my mind, I am thinking somebody is dead for a couple hours; it is going to be okay, we can raise that one.

01:03:11.407 --> 01:03:19.758
But when I saw the bones come back and the skeleton come back, I thought, No way, Lord.

01:03:19.759 --> 01:03:36.798
Is that possible? He said, I did it once. Can you do it again in the new covenant?

01:03:36.799 --> 01:03:42.719
You did it in the Old Testament. Can you do it in the new? Can you do it for us?

01:03:42.720 --> 01:03:54.153
Even greater works will you do? I stretch myself to believe bigger.

01:03:54.154 --> 01:04:06.159
We pray for the sister who had a headache, which is a miracle in itself—we do not want to knock that, and they do not have a headache anymore—but to see somebody that was completely deteriorated come back to life?

01:04:06.160 --> 01:04:39.598
Wow. I give glory to God. Father, we liberate a whole land of Cuba in a day to bring revival all over Cuba, to bring stability financially to Venezuela in these areas, to remove Claudia and bring in a godly man.

01:04:39.599 --> 01:04:51.358
She sold out to the drug lords. Bring in somebody with stability to bring revival across Mexico.

01:04:51.359 --> 01:05:03.025
Father, we are so thankful for Your body. I know that we can do what the Bible says we can do. We can have what the Bible says we can have.

01:05:03.026 --> 01:05:14.302
I thank You, Father, that every single one of these people tonight are believing You for big, that we are not just sitting by watching the sun come up and the sun go down.

01:05:14.303 --> 01:05:19.797
We are more than conquerors, and we are taking the land for You.

01:05:19.798 --> 01:05:28.510
Father, we are telling the people that Jesus Christ is coming, and we are warning them that the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:05:28.511 --> 01:05:34.741
We lay hold to what You said we could have, and we know that by Your stripes we are healed.

01:05:34.742 --> 01:05:46.202
We do not let allergies bother us or trees budding out. Father, I thank You, Lord, that healing belongs to us. Deliverance belongs to us. Our minds are renewed.

01:05:46.203 --> 01:05:53.546
We do not have to have depression, anxieties, fears, night terrors, and things that people say they deal with.

01:05:53.547 --> 01:06:03.562
Why? Because we have perfect peace, whose mind is stayed on You because we trusted in You. We thank You, Lord, for Your body that was broken for us.

01:06:03.563 --> 01:06:10.873
We thank You, Lord, that we are wall-to-wall Holy Ghost and He dwells inside of us richly by faith.

01:06:10.874 --> 01:06:18.045
I believe Jesus Christ dwells on the inside of me and that You speak to me.

01:06:18.046 --> 01:06:25.999
You said we hear Your voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

01:06:26.000 --> 01:06:38.013
My sheep—am I Yours? Are You His? He said, My sheep. That is a level of ownership.

01:06:38.014 --> 01:06:52.639
You are My sheep. You belong to Me. Do you belong to Him? Are you sold out to Him? Is your lamp full of oil? Are you looking for His return?

01:06:52.640 --> 01:06:58.162
Are you the five virgins that have their lamps full and are expecting the return of the Lord?

01:06:58.163 --> 01:07:07.439
Are you the ones that are not? The other five weren't ready. As in the days of Noah, Noah was ready.

01:07:07.440 --> 01:07:17.916
He got on the boat. All the others didn't. There were only eight: his sons, his wives, and him.

01:07:17.918 --> 01:07:25.897
They all got on there. They were so excited to be there. I'm sure the rain's here.

01:07:25.898 --> 01:07:34.639
Prophecy fulfilled as they hear the water arising as in the days of Noah.

01:07:34.640 --> 01:07:44.611
There was an escape from the wrath to come the first time, and I believe there's an escape from the wrath to come the second time.

01:07:44.612 --> 01:07:57.406
He said he wouldn't destroy it by water again, but by fire. We're about to see because the Bible said Jesus told us that as in the days of Noah, so will it be.

01:07:57.407 --> 01:08:14.078
We're getting so close. And so that's why I take this communion to represent something to me: that he has a covenant with me. And I take this body in the name of Jesus.

01:08:14.079 --> 01:08:23.765
And I thank you Lord that my bank account is not lacking anything because you provide for me, that whatever I put my hands to, you provide for me.

01:08:23.766 --> 01:08:30.639
You'll take care of me and you anoint my head and my cup runneth over.

01:08:30.640 --> 01:08:34.771
Surely goodness and mercy will follow me all the days of my life.

01:08:34.773 --> 01:08:40.548
Why? Because I'm dwelling in the house of the Lord forever. I'm dwelling and I'm sitting at your feet.

01:08:40.549 --> 01:08:49.246
And so I take this body in the name of Jesus. And we thank you Lord for your healing power that flows on the inside of me in Jesus'name.

01:08:49.247 --> 01:08:55.052
We take the blood. We make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

01:08:55.053 --> 01:09:01.557
If we confess our sins, he is faithful and just to forgive us of our sins and cleanse us of all unrighteousness.

01:09:01.558 --> 01:09:05.938
I thank you, Lord, that you forgive me of my sins. Thank you, Lord.

01:09:05.939 --> 01:09:10.177
The blood covers us. Thank you, Lord, that the blood covers this atmosphere.

01:09:10.178 --> 01:09:21.198
I plead the blood over me, in my mind, over any visions that you may show me tonight. If not, it's okay.

01:09:21.199 --> 01:09:28.187
Father, we yield, and we see uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:09:28.188 --> 01:09:34.446
We apply the blood of Jesus all around us. And I thank you, Lord.

01:09:34.447 --> 01:09:42.423
I yield to the anointing of the prophet. I yield to the anointing of the watchman. And I yield to it now in the name of Jesus.

01:09:42.424 --> 01:09:49.999
And I thank you, Lord, that you get all the glory and you get all the honor and you get all the praise.

01:09:50.000 --> 01:09:55.284
And if you want to show us anything, fine. If not, we'll just pray over what you've already given us.

01:09:55.285 --> 01:10:03.325
And we're so grateful for all the things you've showed us so far that we see in the news. Thank you, Lord.

01:10:03.326 --> 01:10:09.979
We give you praise and glory, and we give you all of it because you deserve all the praise.

01:10:09.980 --> 01:10:15.240
You deserve all the honor for you are good and your mercy endures forever.

01:10:15.241 --> 01:10:27.197
And we take this blood in the name of Jesus. Amen and amen. Hallelujah.

01:10:27.198 --> 01:10:37.327
Well, let's pray for a little bit here. It's night. It's only Saturday.

01:10:37.328 --> 01:10:51.543
You can pray with me later. Maybe you watch it tomorrow. But I feel we should pray for some things. I talked for a long time, but I'm going to tell you this.

01:10:51.544 --> 01:10:58.079
Bottom line is, if you're watching this and you tell me, Brandon, I've never accepted Jesus Christ as my Lord and personal Savior.

01:10:58.080 --> 01:11:09.999
Before it gets too late, if you're watching this right now, before we pray, I want to ask you, do you know, my friend, do you know Jesus?

01:11:10.000 --> 01:11:21.508
If you were to die tonight, where would you spend eternity? The most important thing I can ever tell you out of any broadcast I ever do is you must be born again.

01:11:21.509 --> 01:11:26.879
Unless a man is born again, he cannot enter into the kingdom of God.

01:11:26.880 --> 01:11:37.040
Unless you know Jesus Christ and confess him as your Lord, you're not going to make it into heaven.

